column9: Hello my name is {{NAME}} and I am a representative of LASG/SEforALL/ETO/Vista. We are conducting a study to understand the usage patterns and quantities of diesel/petrol generators in Lagos state.
column10: Participation in this study is completely voluntary and there will be no payment. You may not directly benefit from this research, however we hope your participation will help to enable the rollout of Distributed Solar Photovoltaic (DPV) systems in a bid to improve electricity access and reliability as well as reduce carbon emission to eventually foster economic growth of Lagos State.
column11: All your information will be stored in password protected files and deleted from our portable devices daily after transferring the data to a secure server. At the end of this study we may publish our findings, however the information will be presented in summary format and you will not be identified in any publications or presentations. All identifiable data will be anonymised after data collection for the study is completed. Also, we will ensure to observe safety protocols and health guidelines such as maintaining six (6) feet distance between us and you (the participant).
